dataLabel: Get 1 example reactome pathway from Wikidata
queryMap:
SPARQL '''PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?item WHERE { ?item wdt:P3937 ?geneid ; wdt:P31 wd:Q4915012 .} LIMIT 1'''@START

dataLabel: Get 10 example reactome pathways from Wikidata
queryMap:
SPARQL '''PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?item WHERE { ?item wdt:P3937 ?geneid ; wdt:P31 wd:Q4915012 .} LIMIT 10'''@START
